OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and low cloud toward the north,
OL,7,Fslowly easing. Brighter spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping toward the south in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with scattered showers, some
OL,10,Fpossibly heavy and thundery. Winds
OL,11,Fgenerally light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers in the south fading,
OL,14,Fas cloudy conditions in the north
OL,15,Fextend southwards, with hill fog
OL,16,Fpatches and the odd spot of drizzle.
OL,17,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
