OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FGradually turning brighter
OL,6,Ffrom the north and mostly dry,
OL,7,Falthough a few light showers are still
OL,8,Fpossible. Winds remaining generally
OL,9,Flight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,13,Fshowers each day, these perhaps more
OL,14,Flikely Tuesday. Turning cooler, with
OL,15,Fovernight rural frost possible in
OL,16,Fsheltered spots. Winds mostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
